{"book": 36, "chapter": 1, "sections": [{"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "當猶大王亞們的兒子約西亞在位的時候，耶和華的話臨到希西家的玄孫，亞瑪利雅的曾孫，基大利的孫子，古示的兒子西番雅。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "耶和華審判的日子"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必從地上除滅萬類。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我必除滅人和牲畜，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "與空中的鳥、海裏的魚，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "以及絆腳石和惡人；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必將人從地上剪除。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我必伸手攻擊猶大"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "和耶路撒冷的一切居民，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也必從這地方剪除所剩下的巴力，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "並基瑪林的名和祭司，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "與那些在房頂上敬拜天上萬象的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "並那些敬拜耶和華指着他起誓，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "又指着瑪勒堪起誓的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "與那些轉去不跟從耶和華的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "和不尋求耶和華也不訪問他的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你要在主耶和華面前靜默無聲，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為耶和華的日子快到。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "耶和華已經預備祭物，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "將他的客分別為聖。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "到了我－耶和華獻祭的日子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "必懲罰首領和王子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "並一切穿外邦衣服的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "到那日，我必懲罰一切跳過門檻、"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "將強暴和詭詐得來之物充滿主人房屋的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：當那日，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從魚門必發出悲哀的聲音，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從二城發出哀號的聲音，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從山間發出大破裂的響聲。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 瑪革提施的居民哪，你們要哀號，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為迦南的商民都滅亡了！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "凡搬運銀子的都被剪除。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那時，我必用燈巡查耶路撒冷；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必懲罰那些如酒在渣滓上澄清的；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們心裏說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "耶和華必不降福，也不降禍。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們的財寶必成為掠物；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的房屋必變為荒場。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們必建造房屋，卻不得住在其內；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "栽種葡萄園，卻不得喝所出的酒。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華的大日臨近，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "臨近而且甚快，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "乃是耶和華日子的風聲；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "勇士必痛痛地哭號。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那日是忿怒的日子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是急難困苦的日子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是荒廢淒涼的日子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是黑暗幽冥、密雲烏黑的日子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "是吹角吶喊的日子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要攻擊堅固城和高大的城樓。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我必使災禍臨到人身上，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使他們行走如同瞎眼的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為得罪了我。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的血必倒出如灰塵；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的肉必拋棄如糞土。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "當耶和華發怒的日子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的金銀不能救他們；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的忿怒如火必燒滅全地，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "毀滅這地的一切居民，而且大大毀滅。"}]}]}